title: BelBivDevoe and the New Cast of New Edition
itunes:title: BelBivDevoe and the New Cast of New Edition
description:
Thursday 1/26- The New Edition series is out so it was only right to have some of the original members "BelBivDevoe" today on the show, as well with the cast members of the series join them for Throwback Thursday. Also, Angela gave some advice to listeners for Ask Yee and it seems like Charlamagne is about to have a recurring Donkey because Sean Spicer got Donkey of the Day again!
